<td valign="top" colspan="2">
<p align="justify"><strong><font size="3">Hatzidimitriou uses American sources to document the destruction of Smyrna</font></strong></p>
<div align="justify">

<!-- JoomlaWorks "AllVideos" Plugin (v2.5.3) starts here -->
