<p><font color="#000000" size="2" face="Arial">On Saturday, May 31, the Pontian Greek Society of Chicago&nbsp;hosted a lecture by Thea Halo entitled <em>The Greek Genocide &ndash; Affirmation and Denial: The Struggle for Historical Accuracy</em> at Duke Realty Corp. Auditorium in Rosemont, Illinois.</font><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font>&nbsp;</p>
