<br /><span><font size="2" color="#000000">On F</font></span></font></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 'Verdana','sans-serif'"><span><font color="#000000" face="Arial">riday May 25, 2007, Professor Theofanis Malkidis gave a lecture at the Cretan Center located at 5941 N. Milwaukee in&nbsp;Chicago. His lecture addressed the historical account of&nbsp;Greek civilization in Pontus and the Pontian Greek Genocide. The lecture&nbsp;highlighted the importance of recognizing the Pontian Greek Genocide not only within the Greek community, but throughout the world.<br />
